data.description: This may be the most charming  home you've seen!  It's like Chip and Joanna Gaines finished it themselves.  Immaculate 3 bedroom, 2  bath ranch home on  .6 acres just minutes from I-270 and down the road from Little Bennett Regional Park and golf course!  You will love this pastoral drive.   This home is perfect for those wanting to get out of townhome, apartment, or condo living - at a reasonable price with a great back yard, a shed, and literally everything has been done in the house.  New systems, hot water heater, and home gym.  Come home to stay with this gem!  It won't last so hurry over.
